      "identifier": "action_contract_split",
      "summary": "Upload action contract is duplicated across protocol and upload service boundaries instead of being shared through one canonical type.",
      "related_files": [
        "goseg/protocol/actions/actions.go",
        "goseg/uploadsvc/adapters/upload_payload_test.go"
      ],
      "evidence": [
        "`goseg/protocol/actions/actions.go` defines `ActionUploadOpenEndpoint`, `ActionUploadReset`, namespace-aware parsing, and `UnsupportedActionError` for protocol actions.",
        "The adapter test constructs payloads using `uploadsvc.ActionOpenEndpoint` / `uploadsvc.ActionReset` and validates `uploadsvc.UnsupportedActionError`, not the protocol action type path.",
